fields.name: Masters Graduated 57mm Golf Tees (25 Pack)
fields.description: Masters graduated tees are made of plastic as it is more durable than wood. They feature a stepped castle design to give a consistent tee height throughout your game. Available in a range of colour coded heights.

fields.name: Callaway Supersoft Golf Balls
fields.description: Callaway Supersoft has been one of the most popular balls for years, with golfers who like it so much that they wonâ€™t play anything else. Now Callaway have combined incredible cover, core and flight technologies to make it even better.

fields.name: Callaway Dual Mark Poker Chip Ball Markers (3 Pack)
fields.description: The perfect accessory on the green, the Callaway Dual Mark Poker Chips are a pack of 3 ball markers with interior magnetic ball markers.

fields.name: Ping G425 Max Golf Driver
fields.description: In the G425 Max Driver, the Max design elevates the moment of inertia to Pings highest level in history and provides golfers the most forgiving driver in golf.

fields.name: Ping G410 Plus Golf Driver
fields.description: The new G410 Plus Driver offer significant advancements in both forgiveness and ball speed and now features movable weight technology.

fields.name: Ping G400 Golf Driver
fields.description: Introducing the G400 Driver, a multi-material design that combines drag-reducing technology with a speed-inducing forged face and MOI-raising tungsten sole weight to deliver longer drives and fairway-finding forgiveness.

fields.name: Under Armour Classic Mesh Golf Cap
fields.description: The Under Armour Classic Mesh Cap is a 'tour worn' item with a structured flex fit design offering protection from the sun. Featuring a mesh construction with Under Armour logo on front and back of the cap.

fields.name: Puma Jackpot Tailored Golf Pants
fields.description: Made from 100% polyester, the Jackpot Tailored Pants are designed with comfort in mind while also promoting better freedom of movement. With a stretch DryCELL moisture wicking fabric, this trouser provides exceptional breathability and moisture management. It also features a new lighter mesh stretch waistband with silicone gripper tape to keep your shirt tucked in.

fields.name: Sunice Tobey Thermal 1/2 Zip Golf Pullover
fields.description: Made from 90% polyester and 10% spandex, the Tobey Pullover is designed to offer maximum comfort and freedom of movement during play. The material transports moisture away from the body and at the same time provides a thermal regulating layer for added warmth in cool conditions.
